      About Aji Tracker
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto text-lg text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      This app was born from my first mischievous feline, Aji - a ginger and white furball 
      with a surprisingly picky palate. Unlike most ginger cats, Aji has his own unique favorites
      that takes me a lot of time to find it out Aji loves chicken more than tuna or salmon. 
    </p>
