      What the pattern is when I gave him that he does not like it, he just skipped over 
      the entire meal and turn around....
    </p>

    <p class="mx-auto text-lg text-center text-gray-400 lg:text-2xl lg:text-left md:text-sm">
      However, using Excel to search and input manually everyday is tedious, and the most important
      is visualization the trends is hard.

      Then, Aji Tracker is aim to solve visualization of amount trends over time and organization
      the favorite table to keep Aji well-fed and live happily everyday.
    </p>
